1. *Vegas* je grad kocke i zabave. (Las Vegas is a city of gambling and entertainment.)
2. Moj prijatelj *vegaše* sve pare na kocki. (My friend gambled away all his money in Vegas.)
3. Da li si ikada bio u *Vegasu*? (Have you ever been to Vegas?)
4. Ova haljina je savršena za *vegas* žurku. (This dress is perfect for a Vegas party.)
5. *Vegasi* su poznati po svojim kazinima i hotelima. (Vegasians are known for their casinos and hotels.)
6. *Vegaske* svetleće reklame su nezaboravan prizor. (The Vegas neon signs are an unforgettable sight.)
7. Planiramo da posetimo *Vegas* sledećeg meseca. (We are planning to visit Vegas next month.)
8. Moj brat je *vegaš* i radi u jednom od najvećih kazina u gradu. (My brother is a Vegas native and works in one of the biggest casinos in town.)
9. *Vegas* je često meta turista iz celog sveta. (Vegas is often a destination for tourists from all over the world.)
10. *Vegaske* noći su duge i vrele. (Vegas nights are long and hot.)